subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution in Iran .
Most territories of Iran except eastern, southern and south-eastern parts ( Fig. 34F ).

Host plants.
Phragmites Adans.
( Poaceae ) (
Wiltshire 1944
).
Comment. Due to unavailability of the coordinates for “Jussufâbâd or Jussufabad”, this locality was excluded from the distribution map ( Fig. 34F ).
